data.description: Come see this beautiful home with a new roof and plenty of space to relax.  Spacious living areas on both floors.  Formal dining room or office on the main level.  Smaller office nook upstairs in the loft area.  All bedrooms are upstairs with a large living area for coming together to watch movies or play games.  All 3 bedrooms are spacious with large closets.  The master bedroom is spacious with 2 separate walk-in closets and a master bath with a separate shower and large garden tub.  The spacious kitchen has plenty of countertop space for cooking.  The breakfast nook is just off the kitchen.  The open concept allows for you to be in your kitchen and still be part of the living room conversation.  Off the kitchen is a large kitchen pantry connected to the laundry area that leads into the 2 car garage.  Nice sized covered patio in the backyard.  Open backyard for kicking a ball around or your pet to run.  Roof replaced in November 2023, Back fence replaced March  2024, Front yard landscaping April 2024, AC/Heater unit replaced in 2019.  Not far from home is Fischer Park with it's many walking & biking trails, fishing pond, splashpad, & playgrounds.
